data.description: MOTIVATED SELLER! Unit 905 features a sunroom with great views and beautiful sunsets.  The two bedroom, two bath condo is sparkling clean and ready for a new owner. This unit has charm and warmth. The kitchen features a breakfast bar, pantry, laminate countertops, and open shelving. Glass shelves partition the living and dining rooms. Flooring throughout is original hardwood. Guest bedroom contains a double closet and access to the hall bath with tub/shower combination. The primary bedroom has an en-suite with separate shower and a large walk-in closet. HOA fees cover utilities except phone. You will enjoy using the pool, outdoor kitchen with grill and herb garden, and courtyard. Amenities include a business center, fitness center with dressing rooms, lounge with catering kitchen, library and card room. Hampshire Towers is located within walking distance of Tanger Center and downtown Greensboro restaurants, businesses and entertainment. Medical facilities and major roads are nearby.
